## 1. About Drivers Against Flock

Drivers Against Flock is a privacy-focused navigation and mapping app designed to help users discover places, view map information, get directions, and choose routes with fewer known ALPR, surveillance, or similar roadside devices.

Drivers Against Flock may provide information about cameras, surveillance devices, routes, places, traffic-related conditions, and other map-based data. This information is provided for general informational and navigation purposes only.

